      propertyPath: objectiveToGive.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0]
      value: Welcome to my desk! Things move a little quicker over here so keep an
        eye out for deadlines!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[1]
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: objectiveToGive.Array.data[0]
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1112463490}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: It is now Wednesday. Welcome to my desk Terry.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: It's been busy here lately so I recommend you talk to the other 3 NPCs
        on this desk. They could probably use your help.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[2].defaultText
      value: However, if you do nothing else, at least **TURN ON THE POWER** by finding
        and pressing the red button.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[3].defaultText
      value: You have 10 minutes (600 seconds), go!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
